info.title: FOOD API
info.description:
**The Food Ingredients Retrieval API** is a powerful and versatile tool designed to provide detailed ingredient information for a wide variety of food products. This API supports multiple input methods including food name, barcode, barcode image, and food image, making it highly adaptable to various use cases in the food industry, health and wellness applications, and consumer services.


**Food Name Lookup:** _Retrieve ingredient information by simply providing the name of the food product._

**Barcode Lookup:** _Fetch ingredients by submitting a food product's barcode._
